Renovation update!!!! Part -1 🪓🧑‍🚒🏠

I have always thought renovations would be easy and fun… but reality check—it’s a whole task! 😅 Choosing colors is overwhelming, picking tiles and flooring feels like a never-ending decision, and selecting cabinets has me questioning every choice! Just when we think something can be done, townhouse challenges pop up. But despite all of it, we’re still so excited to see our vision come to life. 🏡✨

We’ve ripped out the kitchen, gutted the bathroom, and knocked down walls to open up the space. Right now, it’s nothing but bare bones and dust, but soon, this will be a whole new home. Stay tuned! 🚧🔨
